import React, { Fragment } from "react"
import blessed from "blessed"
import { render } from "react-blessed"
import Today from "./components/Today"
import Box from "./components/Box"



const App = () => {

    return (
        <Fragment>
            <Today top={0} left={0} width="50%" height="35%" updateInterval={900000}/>
            <Box label="Recent Commits" top={0} left="50%" width="50%" height="50%"></Box>
            <Box label="Time Log" top="35%" left={0} width="25%" height="65%"></Box>
            <Box label="Pomodoro" top="35%" left="25%" width="25%" height="65%"></Box>
            <Box label="Github" top="50%" left="50%" width="50%" height="50%"></Box>



        </Fragment>
    )
}


const screen = blessed.screen({
    autoPadding: true,
    smartCSR: true,
    title: "Develop Dashboard"  
})


screen.key(
    ["escape", "q", "C-c"],
    () => process.exit(0)
)

render(<App />, screen)
